Summary:
- AnimatedImage now has a daemon background preloader that fills lazy frame caches after playback starts.
- Frame materialization is protected with an RLock so playback and preload do not race the same frame slot.
- Quivi starts preloading when animation begins and whenever resize creates a scaled animated cache.
- This intentionally uses more CPU/RAM after open to reduce first-pass playback stutter.

